{\f0\fs32\b 7. FLOWCHARTS\par}
\pard\sb200\sa200

{\f0\fs24\b 7.1 User Registration Flow\par}
{\f0\fs24
1. User opens registration page\par
2. User enters name, email, password\par
3. System validates input\par
4. System checks if email exists\par
5. If exists: Show error\par
6. If not: Hash password and save to database\par
7. Generate JWT token\par
8. Redirect to home page\par
}

{\f0\fs24\b 7.2 Order Placement Flow\par}
{\f0\fs24
1. User adds products to cart\par
2. User clicks checkout\par
3. System checks if user is logged in\par
4. If not logged in: Redirect to login\par
5. User enters shipping details\par
6. User selects payment method\par
7. System creates order in database\par
8. System clears cart\par
9. Show order confirmation\par
}

{\f0\fs24\b 7.3 Admin Product Management Flow\par}
{\f0\fs24
1. Admin logs in with admin credentials\par
2. Admin accesses dashboard\par
3. Admin selects Products menu\par
4. Options: Add New / Edit / Delete product\par
5. System updates database\par
6. Refresh product list\par
}

