{\f0\fs24\b 8.2 CI/CD Pipeline\par}
{\f0\fs24
{\b Backend Deployment (Azure):}\par
1. Push to main branch\par
2. GitHub Actions workflow triggers\par
3. Checkout code\par
4. Install dependencies (npm ci)\par
5. Deploy to Azure App Service\par
6. Application restarts with new code\par
\par
{\b Frontend Deployment (Vercel):}\par
1. Push to main branch\par
2. Vercel detects changes\par
3. Build React application\par
4. Deploy to Vercel CDN\par
5. Site goes live globally\par
}

{\f0\fs24\b 8.3 Request-Response Flow\par}
{\f0\fs24
1. User interacts with frontend (Vercel)\par
2. Frontend makes API call to backend (Azure)\par
3. Backend processes request\par
4. Backend queries database (MongoDB Atlas)\par
5. Database returns data\par
6. Backend sends JSON response\par
7. Frontend renders data to user\par
}

