\bullet  GET /api/products/:id - Get single product\par
\bullet  POST /api/orders - Create order\par
\bullet  GET /api/orders - Get user orders\par
\bullet  GET /api/admin/dashboard - Admin statistics\par
\bullet  POST /api/admin/products - Add product\par
\bullet  PUT /api/admin/orders/:id - Update order\par
}

{\f0\fs24\b 10.2 Frontend Implementation\par}
{\f0\fs24 The frontend is built with React.js, using functional components and hooks.\par}

{\f0\fs24\b Key Components:\par}
{\f0\fs24
\bullet  Navbar - Navigation header\par
\bullet  ProductCard - Product display component\par
\bullet  CartContext - Shopping cart state management\par
\bullet  AuthContext - Authentication state management\par
\bullet  ProtectedRoute - Route protection for authenticated users\par
}

{\f0\fs24\b 10.3 Authentication Implementation\par}
{\f0\fs24
\bullet  Passwords hashed using bcryptjs\par
\bullet  JWT tokens for session management\par
\bullet  Token stored in localStorage\par
\bullet  Authorization header for protected routes\par
\bullet  Middleware validates token on backend\par
}

