{\f0\fs32\b 15. CHALLENGES & SOLUTIONS\par}
\pard\sb200\sa200

{\f0\fs24\b Challenge 1: Windows App Service Issues\par}
{\f0\fs24
Problem: Node.js application not working on Windows Azure App Service due to IIS configuration issues.\par
Solution: Switched to Linux-based App Service which has native Node.js support.\par
}

{\f0\fs24\b Challenge 2: Azure Policy Restrictions\par}
{\f0\fs24
Problem: Azure Static Web Apps blocked by subscription policy.\par
Solution: Used Vercel for frontend hosting instead.\par
}

{\f0\fs24\b Challenge 3: MongoDB Connection Timeout\par}
{\f0\fs24
Problem: Azure couldn't connect to MongoDB Atlas due to IP restrictions.\par
Solution: Added 0.0.0.0/0 to MongoDB Atlas Network Access whitelist.\par
}

{\f0\fs24\b Challenge 4: CORS Errors\par}
{\f0\fs24
Problem: Frontend couldn't access backend API due to CORS policy.\par
Solution: Configured CORS middleware in Express to allow requests from frontend domain.\par
}

